TalkData.Body: (I did miss a lot of days.)

(Still, I'd rather not get held back...
And make my family worry even more about me...)
(There's a chance that Ena's gonna be at school...)
(An and Toya are also probably pretty worried... If they start asking me stuff...)
(I guess I have to give up...)

(It goes on sale today?
I had no idea.)
I had a feeling that you'd stop by here if you didn't feel like going in for your supplementary classes...

You love Dear Ribbon...
So I thought you'd naturally gravitate towards their new releases.
(What do I do?! What do I do...?!)
(This is how things have to be...)
(I just have to keep running, lose her and...)
<Run if that is what you really want to do.>
<But this may be your last chance to talk to everyone.>
<Or at the very least, to Ena.>
I don't want either to happen...!!!
